，Soojin 现在已与一家名为 BRD Communications 的音乐厂牌签约，这一消息现已得到她新的官方社交媒体账户的证实。</p><p> Soojin于2018年作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cube-entertainment">CUBE Entertainment</a>旗下(G)I-DLE的成员首次出道。 2021 年 2 月，秀珍成为前同学欺凌指控的对象，导致她在下个月休学。 Soojin 将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soo-jin-leaves-gi-dle-group-will-continue-making-music-as-five-members-3019801">2021 年 8 月离开乐队和韩国流行音乐经纪公司</a>。</p><p>退出女团后，秀珍基本上淡出公众视线，直到 2023 年 6 月，她推出个人 Instagram 账户，悄然回归社交媒体。 &#39;Black Forest&#39; will officially mark her first solo music and release since the controversy and her controversial departure from (G)I-DLE.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-gi-dle-soojin-cryptic-teaser-solo-debut-black-forest-3521062">Ex-(G)I-DLE member Soojin teases solo debut with cryptic &#39;Black Forest&#39; video</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
